imdb.plot outline: Power of ten is the name of the new TV game show. The original format of the show is American and was broadcasted on CBS network for first time. The show is one of the most successful TV formats in USA. Each of the episodes from the first season has been watched by more than 10 million Americans. In Bulgaria All Multiplied by Ten will entertained the viewers of the national Nova television. In contrast to most of the similar game shows, in All Multiplied by Ten the participants will have to answer questions with approximately or accurate numbers in percentage. The questions were first an object of sociological research, taken by independent agency. The participant should actually guess what percentages of the inquired people are on considered opinion to the question.
